BEGIN_TEXT

Find the convergence set of the given power series:

\[ \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \dfrac{(x-2)^{n}}{n^{2}} \]

The above series converges for \{ans_rule(10)\} \( \leq x \leq \) \{ans_rule(10)\}.

$PAR

Enter "infinity" for \(\infty\) and "-infinity" for \(-\infty\).

END_TEXT

